import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';

import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import { BsFillHouseFill, BsArrowUp, BsArrowLeft, BsArrowRight, BsArrowDown, BsFillPlayFill, BsFillSkipBackwardFill, BsFillSkipForwardFill } from 'react-icons/bs'


function App() {
  return (
    <body>
      <Container>
        <Row className="p-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button>Push me</Button>
            <Button><BsFillHouseFill/></Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="p-.5">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button><BsArrowUp/></Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="p-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button ><BsArrowLeft/></Button>{' '}
            <Button>OK</Button>{' '}
            <Button><BsArrowRight/></Button>{' '}
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="p-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button><BsArrowDown/></Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="p-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button>Push me</Button>
            <Button>Push me</Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="p-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button><BsFillSkipBackwardFill/></Button>
            <Button><BsFillPlayFill/></Button>
            <Button><BsFillSkipBackwardFill/></Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </body>
  );
}

export default App;
